Package org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.web.reactive

Class ReactiveMultipartProperties

java.lang.Object
org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.web.reactive.ReactiveMultipartProperties
@ConfigurationProperties(prefix="spring.webflux.multipart") public class ReactiveMultipartProperties extends Object
Configuration properties for configuring multipart support in Spring Webflux. Used to configure the DefaultPartHttpMessageReader and the PartEventHttpMessageReader.
Since:
2.6.0
Author:
Chris Bono
